(48460,'A Cockatrice Nuisance',1,19,'You look as if you seek me out with purpose, <career>. Could it be that you have heard of the problems we have encountered with the surrounding unpleasantries that have been waylaying our noble forces? Indeed, they have become quite a nuisance and we would be remiss to ignore them any longer. Please, venture forth and dispatch some of these burdens.','Gethlan Stormwood has asked you to thin out the population of Cockatrice in Avelorn. Return to Gethlan Stormwood when you have slain 10 of the Stonewood Cockatrice.',2241,0,'','[183409,1],[188903,1]',1,0,'48460','',''),
