(48465,'Smash \'Em Humies',2,20,'Oi. Youse look like you ain\'t been in a scrap fer a while. Youse is gettin\' all soft an\' spendin\' all yer time finkin\', just like a runty stunty. Well it\'s time ta get out an\' scrap, wif no worfless finkin\' ta get in da way. Go an\' smash somethin\'! Why? Dere\'s dat \'finkin I warned youse about. Da Boss says smash! Now go \'ave yerself a scrap!','Kill the Empire Guards in Thardrik, return to Grungy Snoutrot when you\'ve had a good scrap.',4314,0,'','',1,0,'48465','',''),
