(49422,'Spring Ahead, Fall Back',2,18,'Oi! C\'mere I gots a job for you. Some twisty humie wots gonna get a taste of my choppa sent me here to check it out. Now I\'s been stuck \'ere fer hours \'cause of that stupid lump and the boss is gonna have me fer breakfast if I don\'t get outta \'ere. So, youse gonna scout the way fer me. Dat\'s right. Dem Portals are supposed to bounce ya to that tower. Youse gonna find out what\'s over there an\' see if der\'s a way out.','Snok Bonebelch requests that you scout the lay of the Twisting Tower and then return to him for your reward.',3046,2925,'','',1,0,'49422','',''),
