(50468,'Welcome Back: On the Battlefield',2,7,'Looking for a little more bloodshed, are we, <name>? Perfect. I have just the task for you. The enemy frequently sends couriers to Altdorf, and they pass not too far from here. Some slip by, but, this time, we\'ve caught one, and used her corpse as a trap. Take this -- it\'s a courier\'s pouch, identical to the one their couriers use. The difference is, this one is full of false information. Since the Empire\'s agents will no doubt try to recover their lost report, they won\'t look too closely at it -- and we will be able to feed the enemy misleading intelligence on our strength and fortifications here. Go out into the battlefield once again and find the courier\'s corpse. Take the courier\'s pouch you find there, and replace it with this one. Do not fail.','Enter the Sea of Claws in Nordland and search the battlefield for the Empire Courier. Interact with the False Reports in your quest inventory in order to place them near the courier\'s corpse. Return to the Raven Warmonger in the Blessed Gathering Warcamp when you are finished.',1930,250,'[207022,1]],choiceitems:[[1005031,1],[1005032,1],[1005033,1],[1005034,1]','',1,0,'50468','',''),
